_header: Make we our plenteous feast of gestening
_description: A couplet translating the text of a Latin sermon (I. Cor. v. 8)

BLRoy8Dx.Transcription:
Make we oure plentevous feste of gystnyngIn clere clennesse and trewe
                    lyuyng
